name: Megan or Brenda
description: My goal is a monogamous relationship leading to a lifelong companionship… I believe that you don’t look for love, but love just finds you when you least expect it, although my friends have finally convinced me to give this a try. They have found somebody Special in their life online, so now I’m here hoping to make a New Friend. I’m a Positive and Happy person and I love to Laugh. I Love Life and I Cherish every moment of it dearly. I’m Candid, Simple and Sincere, Romantic, Kind, Compassionate and Passionate, Sensitive and understanding, Caring and Loyal. I’m Dependable, Trustworthy, Devoted and Affectionate and Genuinely Faithful and the most important qualities I need in a relationship are Security and Safety. I’m looking for a True Lover, friend/companion to complement my life…..
